data.description: Looking for space? You’ll find it here. This cute concrete block home under mature oak shade trees on a quiet street in Avon Park features a split floor plan, with spacious living areas and very large bedrooms. NEW metal roof in 2020, and NEW AC. Guest bathroom was recently remodeled. Tile and linoleum floors throughout the home. Brand new refrigerator, and kitchen has had a makeover with a cute Farmhouse touch. Utility room is inside the home. The fully enclosed Florida room is a bonus space with possibilities for a playroom, sitting, room, or office, etc. Lots of room outside for family get togethers and BBQs!! Schedule your tour and come take a look.
